snippet.title: Kinki Spiritual Affairs Bureau - October 4th 2024 On Steam
snippet.description:
October 4th 2024 On Steam
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2956820/__Kinki_Spiritual_Affairs_Bureau/

Time to fight back against the spirits!
Play as an exorcist with firearms and purge unlawful spirits to solve the mystery of the Saiga village invasion in Nara!

X(Twitter): https://x.com/NotoMuteki
FANBOX: https://notomuteki.fanbox.cc/
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/NotoMuteki?fan_landing=true
